---
// Bottom CTA block before footer
---

<section class="cta">
  <div class="cta-inner">
    <div class="cta-card">
      <h2>Ready to drop persistent admin access?</h2>
      <p>Open source. Self-hosted. Apache 2.0 CLI.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/docs/what-is-jitsudo/" class="btn-docs">Read the docs</a>
        <a href="/docs/quickstart/" class="btn-start">Get started →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2d31;
  }

  .cta-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-card {
    background: #1c1e22;
    border: 1px solid #2a2d31;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f8fafc;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #64748b;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-docs {
    padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #2a2d31;
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 450;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }

  .btn-docs:hover {
    border-color: #4a5568;
    color: #f8fafc;
  }

  .btn-start {
    padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
    background: #f97316;
    border: 1px solid #f97316;
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: #18191b;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .btn-start:hover {
    background: #ea6a00;
    border-color: #ea6a00;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cta-card {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
